The Lew Rockwell Show (podcast) #230

Resist the Police State

Lew interviews Judge Andrew Napolitano about his new book, &quot;It is Dangerous to be Right When the Government is Wrong,&quot; and has an illuminating discussion about the growing culture of the police state in the East German style, here in America.
